kehormatan bagiku.

00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:12.999
Paduka!

00:05:13.373 --> 00:05:15.373
Bukankah itu Paduka?

00:05:18.999 --> 00:05:20.437
Luar biasa!

00:05:24.100 --> 00:05:26.421
Sangat luar biasa!

00:05:59.913 --> 00:06:01.719
<i>Maukah kamu melakukan</i>
<i>semuanya bersama-sama denganku?</i>

00:06:03.398 --> 00:06:03.988
<i>Ya.</i>

00:06:07.656 --> 00:06:09.126
<i>Ayo berbagi segalanya denganku.</i>

00:06:09.843 --> 00:06:11.515
<i>Mari kita berbagi</i>
<i>semuanya bersama-sama.</i>

00:06:18.273 --> 00:06:19.136
<i>Aku takut.</i>

00:06:20.687 --> 00:06:21.921
<i>Janganlah kamu takut.</i>

